Package: modellatoR
Title: Automate the deployment of a statistical model, its testing and
    reporting.
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Antonio Rebordao <antonio.rebordao@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Antonio Rebordao <antonio.rebordao@gmail.com>
Description: A set of utilities to create, setup, train and test a statistical
    model in an automatic fashion. Also generates reports that can be easily
    customized.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.0)
Imports:
    ProjectTemplate,
    randomForest,
    rmarkdown,
    ROCR
Suggests:
    testthat
